        "# рҹӨ– VS Code Docs AI Agent вҖ” Days 1, 2 & 3\n",
        "**Dataset:** `microsoft/vscode-docs` (~780 markdown docs)\n",
        "\n",
        "| Day | Topic |\n",
        "|-----|-------|\n",
        "| 1   | Download & inspect the data |\n",
        "| 2   | Chunk it two ways and compare |\n",
        "| 3   | Build hybrid search (text + vector) |"
      ]
